"I thank you for your quick response and anticipate a successful 
transaction." Phobia inputs Klusters coordinates into the computer 
and begins his decent.

"Computer relay klusters information to my baby in the Predacon 
base." This spider was pushing all the right buttons. either he'd be 
a Predacon hero for helping destroy the base, or a Maximal hero for 
helping fight it off.

--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> ::Kluster::
> 
> Kluster nods, sending Phobia the coordinates of a hatch, which 
begins to open 
> with the press of a button. All exits to that hatch save one are 
locked, 
> Kluster walking off down a corridor. He switches his comm to 
transmit to 
> Hysteria.
> 
> "Hysteria, please meet me in landing bay 1," he says into his comm-
link, then 
> switching it back to Phobia's frequency, "Me and another bot will 
be waiting 
> for you."
